title: SOMA (Patch 2.1.0.3) (GOG)
description:
Install instructions:
- Run "patch_soma_2.1.0.3.exe"
- Play
PLEASE REMEMBER TO SEED, MANY OTHERS WANT THIS! :)
If you like this game, support the developers and BUY IT!

Change log:
Patch 1.03 (13 November 2015)
This update applies minor fixes to SOMA.
Fixed a bug where a tool could get stuck in the player hands.
Fixed a bug where the player got stuck in the shuttle after jumping down with the stun baton.
Added better multi-monitor support.
Mod tool fixes and improvements, including support for snt files. -Modlauncher added to Mac/Linux
